  "description": "Oscar in motion — morph_morph at 0.65, drift high, filter envelope aggressive. The axolotl's gills flicker rapidly as synthesis character shifts moment-to-moment. Short bloom, medium decay — each note has a clear attack then morphs its way through the sustain. MOVEMENT macro cranked so motion is the point, not the pitch. A characterful lead voice.",
